Rust Console Edition: Command Library

Rust Console Edition: Command Library is a powerful extension designed to streamline your Rust Console Edition experience. Easily search and execute commands directly from your browser without needing to switch back and forth between game and guides. With a comprehensive list of commands and items, this tool enhances your gameplay efficiency and helps you stay focused on the action.

Features:

Comprehensive Command List: Access a wide range of commands for Rust Console Edition, categorized for easy navigation.
Search Functionality: Quickly find the command or item you need using the built-in search feature.
Direct Command Execution: Execute commands directly in the game console with just a click.
Items Menu: Browse through all available items and insert them into the game effortlessly.
User-Friendly Interface: Clean and intuitive design that fits seamlessly with your browser.

Installation:

Install the Rust Console Edition: Command Library extension from the Chrome Web Store.
Click on the extension icon to open the commands menu.
Search and select the command or item you want to use.
Execute the command directly in your game console.
